1 Sparcino; his daughter, Jessica Lambert, and her grandson, Hayze Lambert; his son, John
2 Lambert; and his son, Michael Lambert, father of Kaleb Lambert and Alexander Lambert;
3 and
4 WHEREAS, it is fitting and proper for the Legislature of Louisiana to pause in its
5 deliberations to honor the life and legacy of this extraordinary public servant.
6 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Legislature of Louisiana does hereby
7 express its deepest condolences upon the passing of former State Senator Louis Joseph
8 Lambert Jr., and does hereby record its enduring gratitude for his lifetime of service to the
9 state of Louisiana.
10 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to the
11 family of Senator Lambert as an expression of the legislature's sympathy and respect.
